How to schedule a meeting with Michelle via Google calendar

Michelle Greene

08/22/2023

Step 1: From your Barnard email, click on this set of squares:

Step 2: Select the calendar icon:

Step 3: Type my name into the “Search for people” box on the left side:

Step 4: Check my our calendars for mutually agreeable times:

My calendar will say “Busy” at times when I cannot meet.

Step 5: Drag to select the time you want to meet and add Michelle as a guest:

Please only take the amount of time you need.

Step 6: Bask in the glory of some saved time!
